oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Caughran family home
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of the Caughran family home at Holly Grove. William Jesse Caughran (1858-1926) and his wife, Lou N. Preslar Caughran (1858-1912) are on the right. Their son, James Nimrod Caughran (1883-1961), is standing on the left with a dog. William is posed next to a Victrola record player.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Houses; Families; Horses; Phonographs; Dogs
